## Changelog
### Features
* c3a11ca7b168cefe69fef3c9b316e3021d6efb16 feat: Add --pq flag to age-keygen command
* e1e1ec5da588036ed25e36ac3113c85497d37c0e feat: Add support for transcrypt and git-crypt
* 788eb3bb5e9cff42197ebfd908836ee3540401dd feat: Add support for Proton Pass password manager
* 0193146e6309a7f48e18a4dcc13d64ac7c97fe10 feat: Support TOML 1.1
* 3a6d0d65aa3121f7fee863f366a5815b0d1ce352 feat: Switch template function implementation to sprout
### Fixes
* 562f9716b6d3690abd854f6a4ffab73a56595884 fix: Revert to cosign v2.6.1 for release signing
* bc055dfbae3ffcc1b1fee27563cad7f4deb590c5 fix: Ignore templates in exact_ dirs in re-add command
* 4b67af9f58e6a2b827b60fbac58695447244a5d0 fix: Clean paths in external files
* f5f7d0824e3269e703b145632a90aa310128bd58 fix: Reject invalid file and dir names in source dir
* 249d1c9a0bca516290973fa1592e7a6259fe0226 fix: Fix check for adding files in protected directories
### Documentation
* 1a290285fb11328f6238bbf09904fd274028af51 docs: Add link to article
* a99bfe5500ed572a23e2499eacf5bd3aa34332da docs: Fix typo in chezmoi add note
name: v2.69.0
